qas.question: When did the Romans leave Utrecht

answers.text: Around 275 the Romans could no longer maintain the northern border and Utrecht was abandoned
Little is known about the next period 270–650.

qas.question: How was the the church destroyed

answers.text: In ongoing border conflicts with the Frisians this first church was destroyed.
